@endpoint POST /v2/user/customer/offers
@desc Get offer pricing
@required {request: map}
@returns(200) Get the offer proposal considering your current contract
@errors {400: Bad request. (Invalid billing period, invalid offer, etc.). You cannot get a pricing for a free offer., 403: You current contract is not modifiable. Please choose another offer.}

