@required {request: any}
@returns(200) New contract has been created. Some warnings can be present in response.
@errors {400: Bad request. (Invalid billing period, invalid offer, etc.), 403: The contract is not modifiable or the coupon offer has been already used}

@endpoint POST /v2/user/customer/contracts/current/disableAutoRenewal
@desc Schedule termination of your current contract at the end of the commitment.
@required {request: map # Indicate the termination reason}
@returns(204) Your current contract termination has been scheduled
